comment: [Incidental or immaterial] Favors (UTA) grabs Griffin's (LAC) jersey during the rebound.
Mbah a Moute (LAC) sets the screen on Hill (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hill (UTA) makes marginal contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his SQBR.
Favors (UTA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Mbah a Moute (LAC) that does not affect his post move.
Johnson (UTA) and Jordan (LAC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Ingles (UTA) sets the screen on Crawford (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The contact following the screen is marginal.
Jordan (LAC) makes marginal contact with Favors (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Paul (LAC) makes marginal contact with Johnson (UTA) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Redick (LAC) sets the screen on Johnson (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Griffin (LAC) firms up his position and sets the screen on Ingles (UTA).
Redick (LAC) is imminently exiting the lane when the count reaches three.
Favors (UTA) locks Jordan's (LAC) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Jordan (LAC) makes marginal contact with Hill (UTA) off ball.
Paul (LAC) maintains legal guarding position and deflects the ball away from Johnson (UTA).
Hill (UTA) makes body to body contact with Griffin (LAC) that affects his SQBR.
Paul (LAC) makes incidental contact with Hill (UTA) that does not affect his FOM.
Mbah a Moute (LAC) commits a take foul on Hayward (UTA).
Griffin (LAC) commits a take foul on Favors (UTA).
Jordan (LAC) sets the screen on Ingles (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Favors (UTA) is in a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Paul (LAC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Crawford (LAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Johnson (UTA) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Johnson (UTA) released his field goal attempt prior to the game clock expiring is confirmed.
